{"tid":2447374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【慎入】韓國網絡瘋傳中式醃泡菜方法　大叔赤裸浸土黃色混濁泡菜池","createTime":"2021-03-15T07:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T08:43:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af801b66fef1272f785298e9c4b33a7f7ba2b426","tid":2447374,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"近日南韓網上流傳一條「中國大量醃泡菜方法」的影片，片中一名男子半裸地浸在泡菜池，旁邊還有已生鏽挖掘機，池水顏色土黃混濁，嚇倒不少韓國人。<br />\n<br />\n片中可見，製作者會在地上挖出巨大的坑洞然後鋪上塑膠袋，製成巨型泡菜池。之後一名大叔半裸地站在池中，將醃製好的泡菜拋到挖掘機的鏟子中。片中泡菜池的顏色呈土黃又如污水般混濁，且挖掘機都生鏽，看起來極不衛生。<br />\n<br />\n據悉影片早於去年6月在微博上流傳，拍片者自稱是怪手的駕駛員。他當時表示：「我也會醃泡菜，你們吃下肚的泡菜可能就是我醃的」，貼文引起爭議，不久後就被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n另外，韓國網民又發現一條製作泡菜所需的紅辣椒粉影片中，有大量老鼠在辣椒附近游走，場面恐怖。如在微博搜尋「醃泡菜的過程」亦不難發現工人會穿著鞋踩在泡菜上行走。<br />\n<br />\n據南韓農村經濟研究院2020年調查，首爾有54%的餐廳皆使用中國進口泡菜，令網民紛紛擔心泡菜的衛生問題。不過據駐中南韓大使館11日向中國海關總署詢問的結果，影片中的白菜不作出口用途，籲毋需擔心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901251/korea_thumb_20210315_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901251%2Fkorea_thumb_20210315_ch_1024.jpg&h=91c3670d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901251/3_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901251%2F3_1024.png&h=a7d858a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901251/unnamed_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901251%2Funnamed_1024.jpg&h=615ed729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901251/ggg_1024.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901251%2Fggg_1024.gif&h=d6ea6d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KP3xf_A14NI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKP3xf_A14NI&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=f30a337d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KP3xf_A14NI</a>"},{"pid":"6d2e578fc09ae9a1977922a4d94e6aedcd1c41ed","tid":2447374,"uid":315326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">影片中的白菜不作出口用途，籲毋需擔心。</span><br />\n即係支那自己食翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d7377c2370e43aa5d04e66d5aeeb6ba065daf6","tid":2447374,"uid":176960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2e578fc09ae9a1977922a4d94e6aedcd1c41ed","tid":2447374,"uid":315326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">影片中的白菜不作出口用途，籲毋需擔心。</span><br />\n即係支那自己食翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"啲泡菜係for入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6790dcdc364a8366138da35e90d27ca3dae7508","tid":2447374,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}